{"tid":1240931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者遭催淚彈圍困中信大廈　監警會：情況不理想","createTime":"2019-06-18T13:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T08:01:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":479,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"01d385fbfbeb6df9c5803cb2372b6b5e42bca2d5","tid":1240931,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190618/large/1560842094_7876.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190618%2Flarge%2F1560842094_7876.jpg&h=aeb9e0e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上星期三的金鐘衝突，有人拍攝到警方於龍匯道兩端發射催淚彈，大批示威者從一扇狹窄的玻璃門，進入中信大廈躲避。<br />\n<br />\n本台找到當天在現場的示威者親述經歷，他們形容當時情況混亂，一度擔心會人踩人，批評警方封鎖前後防線情況下，依然向示威者發射催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n又指當時身處的位置，是民陣舉行集會的地方，已取得警方不反對通知書，怎料以為安全的地方，會頓時變成危險之地。<br />\n<br />\n警方對事件表示沒有回應。我們又向多名監警會成員展示有關片段，大部分都不予理會，監警會主席梁定邦指，如果事件屬實，情況並不理想。"},{"pid":"c564607c6e1b03d7c7b96892e8d3239b6c129c43","tid":1240931,"uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463666-20190618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463666-20190618.htm&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=7cae3195\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463666-20190618.htm&h=8f06a30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463666-20190618.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5bfceddf900504db723f78e11e15d0f1db441dc9","tid":1240931,"uid":2419,"like":356,"dislike":1,"score":355,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"警方對事件表示沒有回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8f0a9f6a5428263594be9dad25defbb6580a13","tid":1240931,"uid":2419,"li